          "plain_text": "I’m out there with just Christian. It’s windy but clean and there are gentle knee high waves running down the point and the length of the sand bank. I get a few really long waves that are euphoric. Dolphins come to visit and I briefly share a wave with one of them. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
