      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Pap and sausage for dinner is hearty and warm. A candle lit dinner around the fire with a group of people that feel like old friends. More people congregate and before we know it there are guitars, shakers, drums and a didgeridoo. Marco disappears and comes back with an amp and peddle and it turns into a sort of party.",
            "link": null
